{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bab0038acd","title":"关于抚顺市郊发现大批昆虫等的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e38f88467","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"bab0038acd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"124244b8ac","type":"title","text":"关于抚顺市郊发现大批昆虫等的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"},{"id":"71e9beac87","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"},{"id":"de421d3d02","type":"paragraph","text":"请准备在辽东辽西两省全体军民中注射防疫苗。要东其中及京津也要作准备。是否有这样多的疫苗，望告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"},{"id":"83f2459748","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"},{"id":"32e84dfee9","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"},{"id":"b7c0cfd699","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这个批语，写在沈阳3日讯资料（十五）《抚顺市郊发现大批昆虫》上。这份资料说：3月2日下午5时东北军区卫生部接到公安一师的报告，在抚顺市以南70华里的北大沟该师驻地发现大批昆虫等，当即派出检验人员驰赴现场采集标本。据调查该地有大批苍蝇、蜘蝶、跳备，还有一种不知名的黑色小虫，分布成集团状。据该部防疫处负责人称：美军在朝鲜撒布细菌用炸弹和纸袋两种方法，在抚顺发现的苍蝇、蜘蛛等可能是使用后一种方法撤布的。东北军区卫生部已派出30人的防疫队，配合当地政府组成防疫委员会进行室内消毒，并将上述抚顺市以南地带加以封锁。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd"}],"page":{"id":"74b1b56e0d","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bab0038acd","start":477,"end":477}}}},"__N_SSG":true}